assignmentthree

Class EStoreSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignmentthree.EStoreSearch

  • public class EStoreSearch
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines an estore that can be used to store any object that extends the Product class. It offers various methods for the manipulation of the inventory. It should be used with a suitable menu method to call them.
